  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="lightblue" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Despite the real differences between the<BR ALIGN='left'/>tests, each is faithful to the central<BR ALIGN='left'/>purpose of the step transaction<BR ALIGN='left'/>doctrine; that is, to assure that tax<BR ALIGN='left'/>consequences turn on the substance of a<BR ALIGN='left'/>transaction rather than on its form.</TD></TR>
